{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 258 64 "What general formula do the above calcul
ations in  suggest?  2^n" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 172 "2.  Pascal's Triangle.  Recall the definition of \+
Pascal's Triangle.   Use Maple to construct the first 10 rows of Pasca
l's Triangle.  Hint:  Consider the coefficients of   " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 
"(a+1)^n;" "6#),&%\"aG\"\"\"F&F&%\"nG" }{TEXT -1 16 "   rather than  \+
" }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(a+b)^n" "6#),&%\"aG\"\"\"%\"bGF&%\"nG" }{TEXT -1 
291 "  -- even though they are the same.  The trick will be to get the
 coefficients to occur in the correct order.  The Maple command for ge
nerating a sequence might be helpful. It is   seq(expression(i),i=m..n
);   where expression(i) is an expression with index i and m..n is a r
ange of numbers." }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 16 "expand((
a+1)^8);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,4*$)%\"aG\"\")\"\"\"F(*&F
'F()F&\"\"(F(F(*&\"#GF()F&\"\"'F(F(*&\"#cF()F&\"\"&F(F(*&\"#qF()F&\"\"
%F(F(*&F1F()F&\"\"$F(F(*&F-F()F&\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F&F(F(F(F(" }}}{EXCHG 
{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 19 "coeff((a+1)^8,a,3);" }}{PARA 11 "" 
1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#\"#c" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 3 "   " }}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 57 "for n from 0 to 10\ndo seq(c
oeff((a+1)^n,a,i),i=0..n);\nod;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#\"
\"\"" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$\"\"\"F#" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" 
